write a JavaScript program to generate and print out the ascii character and hexadecimal codes for 0 to 7f
Here is an example solution in JavaScript:
```javascript
function getHexCode(char) {
    return ("0" + char.toString(16)).slice(-4);
}

for (let i = 0; i <= 0x7f; i++) {
    let hexChar = String.fromCharCode(i).toUpperCase();
    console.log("ASCII code: " + i, ": Hex Code: ", getHexCode(hexChar));
}
```
